OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIncreasingly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with the chance of
OL,7,Fa few spots of light rain. Mostly dry
OL,8,Flater in the night with clearer spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping, accompanied by freshening
OL,10,Fwinds, but the odd isolated shower
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first, with
OL,14,Fpatchy light rain spreading southeast
OL,15,Fduring the morning. Then turning drier
OL,16,Fand brighter into the afternoon with
OL,17,Fjust a few light showers. Fresh winds
OL,18,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
