OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain clear Sunday morning, then
OL,7,Fbright spells and scattered showers.
OL,8,FDry start Monday, then unsettled and
OL,9,Fchangeable later Monday and Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith the risk of rain or showers.
